{"tid":531495,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO 持有人可否獲居英權 或 轉做 BC ?","createTime":"2018-01-17T01:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T18:50:31.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb915ade9cffdc29a8a7d197d3ca7c9dccbbef0","tid":531495,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"英國：中英聯合聲明仍有法律效力<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1339555-20170701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1339555-20170701.htm&d=KQU5AP42oqIWRdNGrjshz75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=bbc7992c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1339555-20170701.htm&h=dbd91eef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1339555-20170701.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中英聯合聲明內容<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd6.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fissues%2Fjd6.htm&d=KQU5AP42oqIWRdNGrjshz75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=f59d7223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd6.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n雙重國籍問題<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/immigration/chinese_nationality/q4.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2Fimmigration%2Fchinese_nationality%2Fq4.shtml&d=KQU5AP42oqIWRdNGrjshz75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=af58190f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/immigration/chinese_nationality/q4.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"4213cd6fd785c0f7857dccc5ad3109e54afa884c","tid":531495,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f805f667f4aeabce9b4f88d92169ce9df795a0","tid":531495,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:44:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>中英聯合聲明內容節錄</strong><br />\n<br />\n一、凡根據聯合王國實行的法律，在１９９７年６月３０日由於同香港的關係為英國屬土公民者，從１９９７年７月１日起，<strong>不再是英國屬土公民</strong>，但將有資格保留某種適當地位，使其可<strong>繼續使用聯合王國政府簽發的護照，而不賦予在 聯合王國的居留權</strong>。取得這種地位的人，必須為持有在１９９７年７月１日以前簽發的該種英國護照或包括在該種護照上的人，但１９９７年１月１日或該日 以後、１９９７年７月１日以前出生的有資格的人，可在１９９７年１２月３１日截止的期間內取得該種護照或包括在該種護照上。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>雙重國藉問題</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港居民能否持有雙重國籍？<br />\n<br />\n《中華人民共和國國籍法》第3條列明，中國政府不承認雙重國籍身分。但香港在這方面是以<strong>全國人民代表大會常務委員會（人大常委）的「解釋」為準</strong>。這些解釋說明國籍法會怎樣在香港引用。按照人大常委的解釋，香港的中國公民即使已獲得外國公民身分，仍可能會被視為中國公民。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中英聯合聲明是否仍有效</strong><br />\n<br />\n英國回應中國外交部：《中英聯合聲明》仍具效力<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部發表聲明指，《中英聯合聲明》與30年前簽署時，同樣具有效力，聲明具有法律約束力，在聯合國登記並繼續生效，作為共同簽署國，英國政府致力密切監察聲明實施的情況。"},{"pid":"df103c6f2b2a10ed2d53bd18cfda43359beb5d7c","tid":531495,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:48:22.000Z","msg":"比你有居留權你去到有無人請你<br />\n生唔生話到？我驚你連買個老麥都唔識講"},{"pid":"a56132712d33c375496a5ba00c92e02937bc984c","tid":531495,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:52:25.000Z","msg":"好快有居英權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a7ef49e2ee9205607811bcb2c9c46f743a7137","tid":531495,"uid":57914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"df103c6f2b2a10ed2d53bd18cfda43359beb5d7c","tid":531495,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:48:22.000Z","msg":"比你有居留權你去到有無人請你<br />\n生唔生話到？我驚你連買個老麥都唔識講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:53:50.000Z","msg":"大陸仔打個活字都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用拼音定手寫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵你冇BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4c71b6dbbce49d2c82d124446042279d49f6c3","tid":531495,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e9a7ef49e2ee9205607811bcb2c9c46f743a7137","tid":531495,"uid":57914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"sco